omni-channel
experience of transitioning interconnected channels seamlessly and with consistent experience.
Please explain concept 'omni-channel': *what is action between channels *give >=2 descriptions of how this action behaves
User has to correctly identify action between channels (transitioning / switching / moving / flowing between interconnected channels) — score 4/10. User has to correctly give at least two descriptions of how this action behaves (seamless, continuous, consistent, uninterrupted, state-preserving, unified experience across channels) — each correct description contributes 3/10, so 2 descriptions = 6/10. Perfect score math formula: 4/10 + 2 * 3/10 = 10/10.
